---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Quoc Phan - Product Designer"
  description="Product designer passionate about building things. Experience in fintech, CRM, case management, and bioinformatics platforms."
>
  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 px-[50px] py-[202px]">
    <!-- Paragraph 1: Intro - Medium 24px, line-height 1.2 -->
    <p class="w-full max-w-[924px] font-lato font-medium text-2xl text-[#1E1E1E] leading-[1.2em]">
      Hey, My name is Quoc Phan, I'm a product designer and love building things.
    </p>

    <!-- Paragraph 2: Experience - Medium 24px, line-height 1.5 -->
    <p class="w-full max-w-[924px] font-lato font-medium text-2xl text-[#1E1E1E] leading-[1.5em]">
      I've spent the last three years to work on projects in a wide range from fintech including customer relationship management, case management to bioinformatics platforms.
    </p>

    <!-- Paragraph 3: Skills - Light 20px, line-height 1.5 -->
    <p class="w-full max-w-[924px] font-lato font-light text-xl text-[#1E1E1E] leading-[1.5em]">
      I'm already familiar with regulatory constraints and edge cases, and I know how to balance technical, business and a smooth user experience for this type of product.
    </p>

    <!-- Paragraph 4: CTA - Medium 24px, line-height 1.2 -->
    <p class="w-full max-w-[924px] font-lato font-medium text-2xl text-[#1E1E1E] leading-[1.2em]">
      Feel free to contract me!
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
